### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">فَإِذَا قُضِيَتِ ٱلصَّلَوٰةُ فَٱنتَشِرُوا۟ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ وَٱبْتَغُوا۟ مِن فَضْلِ ٱللَّهِ وَٱذْكُرُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ كَثِيرًا لَّعَلَّكُمْ تُفْلِحُونَ</span>

### English

Once the prayer is over, disperse throughout the land and seek the bounty of Allah. And remember Allah often so you may be successful.